Neural Networks. 

Explanation: The paper describes a model that integrates two separate lines of research on computational modeling of the visual cortex, both of which use neural networks to simulate the behavior of neurons in the brain. The model combines a laterally connected self-organizing map with spiking neurons with leaky integrator synapses to achieve both self-organization and segmentation in a unified network. Therefore, the paper belongs to the sub-category of AI known as Neural Networks.
